text: Vojtěch Tomeček (born August 12, 1994) is a Czech professional ice hockey player. He is currently playing for HC Olomouc of the Czech Extraliga. Tomeček made his Czech Extraliga debut playing with HC Karlovy Vary during the 2013–14 Czech Extraliga season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Czech ice hockey right wingers Category:HC Dukla Jihlava players Category:HC Karlovy Vary players Category:HC Olomouc players Category:Piráti Chomutov players Category:Sportspeople from Karlovy Vary
